<div id="outline-container-org5fa1252" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org5fa1252"><span class="section-number-2">11</span> 10 A Brain Possessed</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-11">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>What is the orgin for the phrase "one of us?"</li>
<li>What are some of the early ideas regarding the nature of human epilepsy?</li>
